Mali Panel Sets Funding for 2012 Elections, Minister Says

-- B y   D i a k a r i d i a   D e m b e l e
-- 
2011-09-10T12:59:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-10/mali-panel-sets-funding-for-2012-elections-minister-says.html
A Mali government panel budgeted
30.5 billion CFA francs ($63.5 million) to hold general
elections in April 2012, Budget Minister Sambou Wague said.  The funding is based on estimates of likely voters and
polling stations required for the election, Wague told state
radio yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Diakaridia Dembele in Bamako via Accra at 
 ebowers1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at   asguazzin@bloomberg.net . 